{
  "id": "level-25",
  "title": "Mandatory Feedback",
  "display": "flex",
  "html": "        <div id=\"level-25\" class=\"level-ui hidden flex-col items-center justify-center w-full gap-4 relative mt-2\">\n            <div class=\"text-[10px] sm:text-xs tracking-widest text-orange-500 uppercase font-bold text-center animate-pulse shrink-0\">Mandatory Feedback</div>\n            <div id=\"l25-form-container\" class=\"w-full bg-gray-950 border border-gray-800 rounded-xl p-3 flex flex-col gap-3 overflow-y-auto h-48 sm:h-56 shadow-inner text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-gray-300\">\n                <p class=\"text-orange-400 font-bold text-center border-b border-gray-800 pb-2 mb-1\">Please complete a short customer service satisfaction survey to access the volume controls.</p>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\">\n                    <label>1. Before we begin: Is a hotdog a sandwich?</label>\n                    <select id=\"l25-q1\" class=\"bg-gray-800 text-white rounded p-1 border border-gray-700 focus:outline-none\">\n                        <option>Absolutely yes, it fits the structural definition.</option>\n                        <option>Absolutely not, that is culinary blasphemy.</option>\n                        <option>It is technically a taco.</option>\n                        <option>I am trapped in a volume slider, please send help.</option>\n                    </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\">\n                    <label>2. Overall, are you satisfied with this once in a lifetime gaming experience?</label>\n                    <select id=\"l25-q2\" class=\"bg-gray-800 text-white rounded p-1 border border-gray-700 focus:outline-none\">\n                        <option>Honestly, yes! It's brilliantly creative and fun.</option>\n                        <option>Absolutely not. I hate this with a burning passion.</option>\n                        <option>It's a love-hate relationship, mostly hate.</option>\n                        <option>I will be sending my therapy bills to the developer.</option>\n                    </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\">\n                    <label>3. How would you rate the visual design, UI and physical appearance of the dev?</label>\n                    <select id=\"l25-q3\" class=\"bg-gray-800 text-white rounded p-1 border border-gray-700 focus:outline-none\">\n                        <option>10/10 - Sleek, modern, and visually fantastic.</option>\n                        <option>1/10 - It's clunky, ugly, and hard to read.</option>\n                        <option>It looks great while it's actively torturing me.</option>\n                        <option>I can't see the UI through my tears of frustration.</option>\n                    </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\">\n                    <label>4. What are your thoughts on the background music?</label>\n                    <select id=\"l25-q4\" class=\"bg-gray-800 text-white rounded p-1 border border-gray-700 focus:outline-none\">\n                        <option>It's unironically a great, relaxing track.</option>\n                        <option>It's mind-numbingly repetitive and awful.</option>\n                        <option>I muted my device 15 levels ago.</option>\n                        <option>It perfectly scores my descent into madness.</option>\n                    </select>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"flex flex-col gap-1\">\n                    <label>5. How do you feel about the level design/mechanics?</label>\n                    <select id=\"l25-q5\" class=\"bg-gray-800 text-white rounded p-1 border border-gray-700 focus:outline-none\">\n                        <option>They are clever puzzles that are satisfying to beat.</option>\n                        <option>They are completely unintuitive, poorly designed and the dev needs a new hobby.</option>\n                        <option>Whoever made this is a certified supervillain.</option>\n                        <option>I am just clicking blindly and hoping for 25%.</option>\n                    </select>\n                </div>\n                <button id=\"l25-submit\" class=\"bg-orange-700 hover:bg-orange-600 active:bg-orange-800 text-white font-bold py-3 rounded uppercase tracking-widest mt-2 transition-colors shrink-0 shadow-lg\">Submit to Proceed</button>\n            </div>\n            <div id=\"l25-reward\" class=\"hidden flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6 w-full h-48 sm:h-56\">\n                <p class=\"text-green-500 text-[10px] sm:text-xs text-center font-bold uppercase tracking-widest animate-pulse\">Data Harvested. Thank you.</p>\n                <input type=\"range\" min=\"0\" max=\"100\" value=\"75\" class=\"w-full h-2 bg-gray-700 rounded-lg appearance-none cursor-pointer accent-orange-500\" id=\"l25-slider\">\n            </div>\n            \n            <div class=\"text-4xl font-mono text-gray-300 text-center w-full shrink-0\" id=\"l25-display\">75%</div>\n        </div>"
}
